{
  "stem": "5654.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, camera's ready.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mr. and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dybnis, somehow we never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were split.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because we didn't know where they were, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we mixed with, with-- not only with children, but elderly people which we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was like a-- how can I say?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was no longer a-- a children's home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a transit-- transit camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, in the-- in the [INAUDIBLE], when we arrived in the [INAUDIBLE], we were allowed to go out once a week.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were only allowed to go out with-- with a Swiss Guard walking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they used to take us maybe two or three hours on an excursion in the field, or somewhere like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's about it, you know, just to get our--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the day, we just-- as kids, you know, we made new-- new friends, of course, and we-- nothing much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were watching people behind the-- being a playground, a big playground, it-- it-- it was not barbed wire but it was mesh wires around, so that we were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every now and again, we'd see that the Swiss Guards going and going around and around all the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember that I was-- it was-- Rosh Hashanah came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were talking about-- we were talking about we didn't have enough [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So somehow the elderly people got together and asked the Swiss Guard whether they could allow them to go outside and get some-- some religious thing, [NON-ENGLISH] or [NON-ENGLISH] and-- and tallis, which they did allow.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The only thing we didn't have is a shofar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the story goes at that, I was listening to what was going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
